A case study on the Amazon Top 50 Bestselling Books 2009 - 2019 alongside their authors , genre and number of reviews . 

It was done in excel

Insights :


It was discovered that overall non fiction titiles were more popular than their fictional counterpart with a
n exception in the timeframe of the year 2014 where the later were more popular  . 

There is an overall trend in the cost of books decreasing year over year coinciding with increases popularity .


